    "description": "Cyberwave is a third person wave based arcade survival game with many different gameplay features from different game genres<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight endless waves of enemies in a combat simulator and earn money for upgrades and gear along the way<br><br></li><li>Simple UI and simple gameplay. Simple is sometimes better. Just hop in, shoot some things and have some fun when your bored<br><br></li><li>Non stop action. Apart from the small break in between waves you will have to be on your A-game as the enemies do not stop until you drop or you get out<br><br></li><li>Different types of enemies showing up all the time from ones that explode to ones who have a cloud of poisonous gas around them<br><br></li><li>An arsenal of weapons to choose from. Choose from many different weapons or go in with your bare hands its up to you.<br><br></li><li>Many characters to choose from who all have their own ability they can use to aid you<br><br></li><li>Physics and Gore enabled. Its a game all about killing things and feeling powerful. Why not have the ability to send chunks of enemies flying all over the place</li></ul>",
